<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>9 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RT-8609 SERIES - INSTALL - SLAVE VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="4">
        <title>SLAVE VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If previously removed, install the air line fittings on the slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n5">Figure 235</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n5" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n5" filename="../figg13/g13029n5.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 235. Install Air Line Fittings on Slave Valve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the spring on the shank of the actuating pin and insert in the bore of the
                transmission case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n6">Figure 236</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n6" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n6" filename="../figg13/g13029n6.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 236. Install Spring on Shank of Actuating Pin</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the hat-type alignment sleeve in the bore of the slave valve (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n7">Figure 237</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n7" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n7" filename="../figg13/g13029n7.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 237. Install Hat-Type Alignment Sleeve</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position gasket on the valve mounting surface and install the slave valve on the case,
                inserting the end of the actuating pin into the alignment sleeve. Secure the valve to the case with four
                bolts. Apply Loctite 242 or equivalent to the bolt threads. Tighten evenly to 8 to 12 ft-lbs. (11 to 16
                N&#8226;m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n8">Figure 238</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n8" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n8" filename="../figg13/g13029n8.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 238. Secure Valve to Case With Bolts and Tighten</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
